-You look pretty again.

294
00:12:40,650 --> 00:12:41,410
Thank you.

295
00:12:41,410 --> 00:12:42,740
You look beautiful too.

296
00:12:44,410 --> 00:12:45,940
-You scared me.
-Lu Xixiao!

297
00:12:46,010 --> 00:12:47,480
