512
00:23:55,570 --> 00:23:57,980
You were always away.

513
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:58,800
I'm sorry.

514
00:23:59,230 --> 00:24:00,050
Honey.

515
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:06,150
I'm sorry.

516
