571
00:28:40,410 --> 00:28:41,330
you were thinking every day

572
00:28:41,330 --> 00:28:42,930
about how to break up with me.

573
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:50,570
I already made it

574
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:52,140
