757
00:40:02,930 --> 00:40:04,260
Stop worrying about me.

758
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:05,560
Zhou Wan,

759
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,890
put down

760
00:40:06,890 --> 00:40:07,600
