780
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:00,690
I found it.

781
00:41:07,410 --> 00:41:08,120
Don't worry.

782
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:09,730
I've already spoken to Mr. Lu.

783
00:41:09,730 --> 00:41:10,560
If there are any issues,

784
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:11,760
