802
00:42:38,370 --> 00:42:39,080
Zhou Wan,

803
00:42:39,850 --> 00:42:41,160
so the one you want to deal with is

804
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:42,080
Lu Zhongyue.

805
00:42:43,290 --> 00:42:44,560
Is that why you said

806
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,250
